      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Raiton)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 3</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 3</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 15 | <b>Successes:</b> 1</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 3 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 14</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> S</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>The subject is knocked @Condition[prone]{prone}, becomes @Condition[staggered]{staggered} and cannot run or charge, all for 1 round. You can delay the effects for up to 3 rounds, chosen when you perform the technique. The effects will take place during your turn in the chosen round.</p>\n\n\n\n",
